nodes.title: PainterI2V
widgets_values:
# Motion Amplitude Reference

## Direct Values
- **`motion_amplitude = 1.0`** → behaves like original node (**0% boost**)  
- **`motion_amplitude = 1.15`** → default; **~+15% motion**, general use  
- **`motion_amplitude = 1.3`** → **~+30% motion**, sports  
- **`motion_amplitude = 1.5`** → **up to +50% motion**, extreme motion  

---

## Recommended Ranges by Activity
### Fast Motion (running / jumping)
- **`1.25–1.35`**

### Normal Motion (walking / waving)
- **`1.10–1.20`**

### Subtle / Slight Boost
- **`1.00–1.10`**
